### Pokemon Battle API

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Root - API information

GET {{baseUrl}}/ HTTP/1.1

### Health check

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/health HTTP/1.1

### Get Pokemon by name

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/pokemon/pikachu HTTP/1.1

### Get another Pokemon

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/pokemon/charizard HTTP/1.1

### List all Pokemon (with pagination)

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/pokemon?limit=10&offset=0 HTTP/1.1

### Start a battle between two Pokemon

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/battles HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pokemon1_name": "pikachu",
  "pokemon2_name": "charizard"
}

### Start another battle

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/battles HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pokemon1_name": "bulbasaur",
  "pokemon2_name": "squirtle"
}

### Get battle by ID

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/battles/1 HTTP/1.1

### List all battles (with pagination)

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/battles?limit=10&offset=0 HTTP/1.1
